Connections:
Pin 2- 5v - Relay
Pin 4 -5v - Soil Moisture Sensor Amplifier
Pin 6- GND - Relay D0
Pin 9- GND - Soil Moisture Sensor Amplifier
Pin 38 - GPIO 20- IN -Relay A0
Pin 40 - GPIO 21-OUT - Soil Moisture Sensor Amplifier

Source code:
